      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm still logging on. everything just feels... finished. the lab results came back again and it’s just another dead end. after five years of this, i realize there’s nothing left. no funding, no data, no future. i’m just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i just want it all to be quiet. i just want to stop feeling like i'm running on a treadmill that's about to break.",
