    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"permanent stillness\" sounds... almost peaceful compared to this. Like, I'm so burnt out that even sleep doesn't feel like enough anymore. Everything is just so loud and heavy. Do you think it's actually wrong to want that? To just want to opt out because there's nothing left to fight for?",
